textMap.PRIMARY: Have Yourself a Merry Little Christmas
Joel de la Fuente: Joel de la Fuente made his New York Philharmonic debut in the role of Claudio in Berlioz's opera Beatrice et Benedict.
Bella Heathcote: Former Australia National Theatre Drama School student (2008) and winner of the 2010 Heath Ledger Award.
Rufus Sewell: Has a son named William Douglas Sewell (Billy), born 18 March 2002 with Amy Gardner
Chelah Horsdal: Opting to use a reusable container she never consumes bottled water on set.
